+++ An addictive incremental game about particle physics research +++
Run your own laboratory, collect data, hire physicists, and make historic discoveries!
Data is necessary for research. You can collect data by clicking on your detector. Once you hire physicists, they will also collect data for you.
In Particle Clicker, you can research many interesting particles.
Every time your lab researches something, it becomes more popular. This "reputation" guarantees you a constant stream of funding in form of "jetons" (JTN), the coins used for buying coffee at CERN.

PhD students, Postdocs, Professors and many more are the types of workers you can hire in Particle Clicker to make your academic life easier. They will ease the tedious task of collecting data for you so you can focus on your research.
